abstract: Lesia Tsurenko and Urszula Radwanska advance to final at Istanbul Cup; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Lesia Tsurenko of Ukraine beat Kirsten Flipkens and Urszula Radwanska of Poland beat Magdalena Rybarikova to set up the final. Each player will be seeking her first WTA singles title.

headline.main: Istanbul Cup Final to End With a First Win
